l'adorable voisine who is to say what love really is ? this is a christmas story that may have a more halloween feel . shep henderson takes a new apartment . little does he know that the other residences are witches . gil holroyd kim novak sort of likes shep and wonders if she can get his affection without witchery . she also finds that shep 's girlfriend ( janice rule ) is an old adversary . now the fun begins . will gill get shep ? will shep find out that gill is a witch ? who is to say what love really is ?